headline: Does Accenture’s Recent Slide and GenAI Growth Signal a Market Opportunity for 2025?
summary: If you have been keeping an eye on Accenture, you are not alone. With the stock closing recently at $256.17, it is natural to wonder if the current price is a bargain, a stall, or a signal for bigger moves ahead. Over the past year, Accenture’s shares have taken investors on a bit of a roller coaster, down 23.3% over the past twelve months and a steeper 26.6% year-to-date.
